\nc<>(Reina... accepting advertising requests without consulting
me first) (What are you thinking...)
\nc<Advertiser>It's an honor to meet you, Levantia-san.

\ncAs I mentioned briefly in the email, we would like you to
eat and promote our company's cup ramen in a scene.

\nc<>(Wha... what is this... it's too salty and not delicious at
all...!!)

\nc<>(But because it's an advertisement...) U-um...! The seafood
flavor is really coming through, isn't it...?
\nc<Advertiser>Anyway, please give us a closing comment~.

\nc<>Haa... let's eat together and fight against the
villains...! R-Ramen is definitely Nisson Matcha Ramen...!!

\ncPlease give us a brighter expression~ One more time! One
more take!

\nc<>Let's eat together and fight against the villains! Ramen is
definitely Nisson Matcha Ramen!
\nc<>I obtained the memory of the Matcha Ramen Advertisement.
